{"about_the_game":"N.O.D.E. is a puzzle platformer in 2.5.D that redefines the genre with its Timeline-based navigation. In this engaging and atmospheric adventure you guide your robot on a journey through enigmatic remains of a top-secret Soviet nuclear complex.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>PLAN, STRATEGIZE, EXECUTE</strong></h2>- Plan your robot\u2019s route by examining the Nuclear Plant blueprints and considering the information and clues you have found.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757670/extras/mapSequence.gif?t=1739425177\" /><br><br>- Create a sequence of commands on a Timeline for your robot to navigate between checkpoints.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757670/extras/constructTimeline.gif?t=1739425177\" /><br><br>- Execute the Timelined commands, witness the results, and adjust to solve the puzzle. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757670/extras/planExecuted.gif?t=1739425177\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>ENGAGING AND ATMOSPHERIC</strong></h2>Immerse yourself in a world where Cold War era historical intrigue meets science fiction, delivered by rich imagery and intricate level design.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757670/extras/atmosphere.gif?t=1739425177\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>BRANCHING DIALOG</strong></h2>Live the story through dynamic dialogues with branching paths. Shape the narrative as you progress. Make decisions that impact the course of your journey. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757670/extras/branchingDialog.png?t=1739425177\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>FIND SECRETS</strong></h2>Explore beyond the main path and find hidden challenges. Uncover secrets and easter eggs. Dive in deeper narrative laye